        <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• The Cube Gallery:</b> A dynamic space for rotating exhibits and events that inspire and connect.
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Premium Offices:</b> Sleek, future-forward workspaces for innovators and visionaries.
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Retail Spaces:</b> Ground-level retail opportunities for luxury boutiques benefitting from a prime location with exceptional foot traffic.
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Luxury Condos:</b> Two exquisite apartments featuring premium appliances, expansive private entertainment terraces, and seamless indoor-outdoor living.
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Private Club:</b> An exclusive members-only hub for networking, events, and social gatherings.
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Innovation Hubs:</b> Cutting-edge incubators with rooftop gardens—perfect for collaborative indoor-outdoor work.
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Media Suites:</b> Two fully-equipped professional editing bays for media professionals, complete with the latest technology and amenities.
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Gourmet Dining:</b> Two thoughtfully curated premium restaurants perfect for both fine dining enthusiasts and business lunches.
        </div>
