        <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Required Investment:</b> $40,000,000 USD
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Floors:</b> 8 floors plus a 28-car garage basement
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Square Meters:</b> 4972 m² of rentable space
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Square Feet:</b> 53,518 sq ft of rentable space
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Monthly NOI (Net Operating Income):</b> $311,374 USD
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Yearly NOI (Net Operating Income):</b> $3,576,492 USD
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Capitalization Rate (Cap Rate):</b> 8.94%
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <b>• Yearly Potential Cash Flow:</b> $4,012,492+ USD
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
